Adds a widget to display the status of an AO Speak channel in Wordpress.

== Description ==

WARNING
This is an alpha plugin, not ready for production use. Use with caution.

This is a first draft, it will be completed as features are developped.

= Including: =
* Stuff
* More stuff

== Installation ==

Requirement
PHP 5.2.12 with CURL

1. Upload the plugin to the `/wp-content/plugins/` directory
2. Activate the plugin through the 'Plugins' menu in WordPress
3. Add a widget to one of your template's sidebar is supported

== Remove plugin ==

1. Deactivate plugin through the 'Plugins' menu in WordPress
2. Delete plugin through the 'Plugins' menu in WordPress

It's best to use the build in delete function of wordpress. That way all the stored data will be removed and no orphaned data will stay.

